msgstr "모듈 내용"

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:14
msgid "Bases: :py:obj:`django.contrib.postgres.fields.HStoreField`"
msgstr "기본: :py:obj:`django.contrib.postgres.fields.HStoreField`"

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"Drop-in replacement for Django's ``HStoreField`` with the custom widget."
msgstr "맞춤 위젯이 있는 Django의 ``HStoreField`` 대체."

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:19
msgid ""
"Overrides ``formfield()`` so that the admin and ModelForms automatically use"
" :class:`~django_hstore_widget.forms.HStoreFormField` and "
":class:`~django_hstore_widget.widgets.HStoreFormWidget` -- no manual form "
"configuration required."
msgstr ""
"관리자와 ModelForms가 자동으로 :class:`~django_hstore_widget.forms.HStoreFormField` 및"
" :class:`~django_hstore_widget.widgets.HStoreFormWidget`을 사용하도록 "
"``formfield()``을 재정의합니다 -- 수동 폼 구성 불필요."

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:25
msgid "Example"
msgstr "예시"

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:38
msgid "Return a form field class pre-configured with the custom widget."
msgstr "맞춤 위젯으로 사전 구성된 폼 필드 클래스를 반환합니다."

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:0
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "매개변수"

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:40
msgid ""
"Keyword arguments forwarded to the form field constructor. Pass "
"``form_class`` or ``widget`` to override the defaults."
msgstr ""
"폼 필드 생성자로 전달되는 키워드 인수. 기본값을 재정의하려면 ``form_class`` 또는 ``widget``을 전달하세요."

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:0
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "반환"

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:44
msgid "A form field instance wired to the hstore widget."
msgstr "hstore 위젯에 와이어링된 폼 필드 인스턴스."

#: ../../autoapi/django_hstore_field/fields/index.rst:0
msgid "Return type"
msgstr "반환 타입"
